title: Diebold
description: Diebold's brand colors are a blend of deep blue (007DC3), dark blue (003F69), terracotta (954010), steel grey (445C6E), forest green (005238), and antique gold (97824B). These colors represent the brand's focus on innovation, security, and reliability in the financial technology sector. The information about these specific colors was sourced from a design document available at http://www.tomsieron.com/wit/pin/assets/Diebold.pdf.
